competitive and is rated at a good level. The department also has university level Regional Biotechnology Research Centre with special focus on the research areas such as Plant Biotechnology, Medical Microbiology, Industrial Microbiology, Medicinal Plants, Genetics and Molecular Biology. Department is in the process of establishing the excellent infrastructure needed to carry out challenging experiments in emerging areas of life sciences. The department has an excellent reputation in Biotechnology teaching. The Department has Career Oriented Course in Plant Tissue Culture i.e certificate course, Diploma course and Advanced Diploma course in plant tissue culture for the Biotechnology Students. Faculty Profile Courses Activity Link Newspaper Merit List Gallery --> Sr. No. Name of the Staff Designation Qualifications Subject Taught Experience Profile Photo Contact No. Email ID 1 Dr. Nilesh V. More Head of Department M.Sc., Ph.D. (Biotech.) Cell Biology, Biochemistry 19 Years 8329502899 nileshm2002@gmail.com 2 Dr. Abhaykumar Kamble MV Asst. Professor M.Sc., Ph.D. (Biotech.) Plant Biotechnology, Bio-instrumentation 14 Years 9986884498 abahy.gene@gmail.com 3 Dr. Kanakchari Moglichera Asst. Professor M.Sc., Ph.D. (Biotech.) Medical Biotechnology, R-DNA Technology 11 Years 6302702837 chari.biotech@gmail.com 4 Mr. Kishorkumar P. Maknikar Asst. Professor M.Sc. (Biotech.), ICAR-NET Computational Biology, IPR 18 Years 9764670197 Kishormaknikar@gmail.com 5 Ms. Madhuri H. Shendge Asst. Professor M.Sc. (Micro.), CSIR NET Microbiology, Immunology 07 Years 8999254114 madhurishendge20@gmail.com 6 Mr. Sharad C. Gangavane Asst. Professor M.Sc. (Biotech.), CSIR-UGC NET Genetics, Molecular Biology 16 Years 8421174635 Sharadbiotech1986@gmail.com 7 Mr. Anand H. Waghmare Asst. Professor M.Sc. (Biotech), B.Ed. PTC, Plant Biotechnology 03 Years 9823409632 waghmareanand37@gmail.com 8 Mr. Balasaheb A. Jadhav Asst. Professor M.Sc. (Biotech) Environmental Biotechnology, EVS 5 Years 937330098 bala